Ticket 2: Bug Report
Title: "Delete" button removes meetings instantly without asking 
Priority: High
Severity: High
Description: The app is supposed to double-check with the user before deleting anything important. Right now, if I click the delete button by mistake, the meeting vanishes 
forever with no warning.

Steps to Reproduce: 
    1. Open the application and go to the Meeting List tab.
    2. Find any existing meeting record in the list.
    3. Click the Delete button

Actual Result: The meeting is removed from the list and the database immediately without any warning or popup window.

Expected Result: A confirmation dialog must appear asking the user to confirm the destructive action before the meeting is deleted. The meeting should only be removed 
if the user clicks "Confirm" in that popup.
